Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:33.66,电波诚译,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(617.333,666)}{\fad(500,0)}第二季 第七集
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 学校有什么新鲜事吗  - 没有\N{\fs38}- What's new at school? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 呃 有个盛饭的阿姨死了\N{\fs38}Nothing! Oh, uh, one of the lunch ladies died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在体育馆被发现的 脖子上有两个洞\N{\fs38}They found her in the gym with, like, two holes in her neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.71,0:00:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血被吸干了\N{\fs38}and all the blood drained out of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天 谁能做出这种事情\N{\fs38}Good lord! Who does something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显然是吸血鬼啊 胡椒呢\N{\fs38}Obviously a vampire. W-w-where's the pepper?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 吸血鬼真的存在吗\N{\fs38}Wait, what?! Vampires are real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是真的 谁知道呢\N{\fs38}Yes, Summer, vampires are real. Who knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.22,0:00:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦对 所有人都知道 几百年了都\N{\fs38}Oh, right, all humanity, for hundreds of years, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 宇宙之大 无奇不有\N{\fs38}Yeah, Summer, it's a big universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.40,0:00:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点习惯吧 对吧 Rick\N{\fs38}Get used to it. R-right, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们要怎么办\N{\fs38}Well, what are we going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直活着 到死为止\N{\fs38}We're gonna live our lives until we die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能被吸血鬼吸干\N{\fs38}Possibly by vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.99,0:00:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更可能被车撞扁 或者心脏病而死\N{\fs38}More likely auto accident or heart disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也还是可能死于吸血鬼\N{\fs38}but possibly vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外公 你能不能动用你超人的智慧\N{\fs38}Grandpa Rick, couldn't you, like, use your superknowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.38,0:00:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成青少年混进我们学校\N{\fs38}to turn yourself into a teenager and come to our school
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.21,0:00:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我们抓住这只吸血鬼\N{\fs38}and help us hunt the vampire down?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 你这\N{\fs38}Um-- wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.29,0:00:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想得还挺详细\N{\fs38}Yeah, pretty specific pitch, Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.73,0:00:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我兴许可以变成青少年\N{\fs38}I probably could turn myself into a teenager
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混进满是青春痘和荷尔蒙\N{\fs38}And hang out in the zit-covered, hormone-addled,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低端垃圾横行的狗屁中学\N{\fs38}Low-stakes assworld that is high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\an8}Low-stakes testing在教育测试体系内是一种结果较为宽松 竞争压力小的评分系统
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要反问一句\N{\fs38}But here's my reverse ask--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我[哔]为什么要这么做\N{\fs38}Why in the [bleep] would I ever do that, ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.76,0:01:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你凭什么要求我这么做\N{\fs38}And how dare you even ask me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样也算是恬不知耻了\N{\fs38}And why aren't you more ashamed of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸\N{\fs38}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要知耻 宝贝\N{\fs38}Be ashamed of yourself, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jerry 你意识到你刚对女儿说了什么吗\N{\fs38}Jerry! Do you know what you just said to our daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 刚才我没在意\N{\fs38}Sor-ry! I wasn't paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在意关于吸血鬼的事情吗\N{\fs38}To a conversation about vampires?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明显 我不知道是吸血鬼的事情\N{\fs38}Clearly, I didn't know it was about vampires,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.71,0:01:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我就没注意\N{\fs38}Because I wasn't paying attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是对我上点心\N{\fs38}Which you would know, if you ever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就该知道我刚才没注意\N{\fs38}paid attention to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了 这就进入受害者的角色了\N{\fs38}Oh, here we go, right to the victim role.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是个受害者\N{\fs38}Am I a victim, Beth,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.66,0:01:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是娶了一个恶毒无比\N{\fs38}Or am I married to a mean, unfair monster
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.21,0:01:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还总是伤害我的魔鬼\N{\fs38}That always hurts me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天爷\N{\fs38}Jesus christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.82,0:01:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要是解决不了婚姻问题 赶紧离婚了事\N{\fs38}Will you fix your marriage or get a divorce already?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.08,0:01:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们试过一次婚姻咨询\N{\fs38}Well, we tried a couples' therapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是地球上的心理咨询\N{\fs38}That's earth therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.66,0:01:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好比找一匹马来修旋转木马\N{\fs38}You might as well ask a horse to fix a merry-go-round.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.81,0:01:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它再怎么想努力\N{\fs38}I mean, he'll try his best, but mostly,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能被吓坏而已\N{\fs38}He's just gonna get horrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.73,0:01:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道外星球有一个百分百成功的地方\N{\fs38}I know about a place off-planet with a 100% success rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也想让婚姻继续啊 如果我们能的话\N{\fs38}Well, we want to make it work, if we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.49,0:01:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 但是  - 那就这么定了\N{\fs38}- It's just..  - Then it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.82,0:01:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用打包衣物了\N{\fs38}No need to pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发出发出发\N{\fs38}Let's go, go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得老爸和老妈\N{\fs38}Do you think mom and dad are, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会离婚吗\N{\fs38}Gonna get a divorce?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想想还是可以的\N{\fs38}I think it's okay to dream, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去做几根木钉\N{\fs38}I'm gonna go make some wooden stakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在婚四所给你们定了两天的强化治疗\N{\fs38}I booked you for a two-day intensive at Nuptia Four,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他家是银河系里最好的婚姻咨询机构\N{\fs38}The galaxy's most successful couples' counseling institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们甚至可以挽救\N{\fs38}They could save the marriage of a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗和巧克力的婚姻\N{\fs38}and a bar of dark chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个色情影星的婚姻\N{\fs38}They could save the marriage of a porn star and a porn star.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我是愿意试一试的\N{\fs38}Well, I know I'm ready to try whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这话是说我不愿意咯\N{\fs38}Which clearly implies that I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是要比什么 Beth\N{\fs38}It's not a competition, Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打赢嘴仗的策略就是\N{\fs38}Oh is that how you're gonna try to win,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗示说我太争强好胜是吧\N{\fs38}By implying I'm competitive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你不是吗\N{\fs38}If the shoe fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是你妈个头  - 呵呵\N{\fs38}- My shoe fits up your ass. - You wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们咨询愉快 周四见\N{\fs38}Okay, have fun. See ya Thursday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:02:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼\N{\fs38}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这老混蛋\N{\fs38}Jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说我爸\N{\fs38}Don't insult my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了他的基因 我们的孩子才只是半蠢而不是全蠢\N{\fs38}He's the reason our kids are only half-stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.86,0:03:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 你刚才说自己\N{\fs38}Ha! You just called yourself --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了\N{\fs38}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Smith夫妇吗  - 是的\N{\fs38}- Beth and Jerry Smith? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Glaxo Slimslom\N{\fs38}I'm Glaxo Slimslom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到婚四所\N{\fs38}Welcome to Nuptia Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里能解决你们婚姻的烦恼\N{\fs38}Your marriage can rest easy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jerry 坐在这里 把这个戴上\N{\fs38}Jerry, go ahead and sit there and put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个仪器可以扫描提取你大脑中\N{\fs38}This machine isolates the part of the subject's brain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于你对配偶的感知\N{\fs38}Containing all perceptions of its romantic partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在扫描Jerry对Beth的感知\N{\fs38}And we will now render Jerry's perception of Beth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并具体化为人工生物的形象\N{\fs38}With artificial biological life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个有意思\N{\fs38}Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么玩意 收回你的想法\N{\fs38}What the hell is that?! Take that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然把我想成这样\N{\fs38}You do not think that about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没做啊\N{\fs38}I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们把我的想法扫描出来了\N{\fs38}They scanned it out of my brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能收回那个想法吗\N{\fs38}Can I take it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好后悔的\N{\fs38}There's nothing to regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是要处理这些无意识 不健康的想法\N{\fs38}We're dealing with unconscious, unhealthy thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该你了\N{\fs38}Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在扫描Beth对Jerry的感知\N{\fs38}Now, we scan for Beth's perceptions of Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使劲扫 他于我与死人无异\N{\fs38}Scan hard. He's dead to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么对你来说都是死物吧\N{\fs38}Everything's dead to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你再说一遍  - 没事\N{\fs38}- What? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看看 一边哭去吧\N{\fs38}Read it and weep, bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都看到我是什么意思了吧\N{\fs38}Does everybody see what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个的意思 大家都看得很清楚\N{\fs38}I think we all see what you both mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼的事有什么进展吗\N{\fs38}Any leads on the vampire?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 我是说\N{\fs38}No, Summer! I mean, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就别再在意这事情了\N{\fs38}I think it might be time that we just l-let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这没什么大不了\N{\fs38}Oh, so, now, you're too cool for this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为外公也这么想吗\N{\fs38}Just because grandpa Rick is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为这个 宇宙实在太大了\N{\fs38}It's not that, it's just that the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要在意这么微不足道的事\N{\fs38}is a little too big to care about something so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊\N{\fs38}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好啊 小海辛们\N{\fs38}What up, my Helsings?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\an8}范海辛是著名的吸血鬼猎人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁想来猎杀吸血鬼 哈哈\N{\fs38}Who wants to hunt a vampire? Ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rick 你 你怎么\N{\fs38}Rick? How-- how did you--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才无聊来着 然后想起来\N{\fs38}Yeah, I got bored and then, I remembered,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早我回绝了Summer 然后我寻思\N{\fs38}This morning, how I blew Summer off, and I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛非得跟个老混蛋似的\N{\fs38}Hey, why are you such a grumpy douche, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧到车库里\N{\fs38}Go to the garage,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己的思维传输到少年的克隆体\N{\fs38}transfer your mind into a younger clone of yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后加入到年轻人的狂欢里吧\N{\fs38}and get embroiled in some youthful hijinks,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么大不了的\N{\fs38}What's the BFD?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就来了 我是小Rick\N{\fs38}So here I am. I'm tiny Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好吧\N{\fs38}O-o-okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了就好 Rick\N{\fs38}Well, it's good you're here, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们自己肯定搞不定\N{\fs38}I was pretty sure we didn't have what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个吸血的东西的\N{\fs38}to deal with a bloodsucker on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别妄自菲薄 Summer\N{\fs38}Don't short-sell yourself, Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完全能做到 但是我们[哔]组队的话\N{\fs38}You got everything it takes. But it'll still be fun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是很有趣啊 小Rick[哔]无敌\N{\fs38}To do this as a [bleep] team, mother[bleep] tiny Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天呐 Toby Matthews来了\N{\fs38}Oh, my god, Toby Matthews!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 我是小Rick 我新来的\N{\fs38}Hey, Toby. I'm tiny Rick. I'm new.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:05:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别欺负我哦 哈哈 开玩笑的\N{\fs38}Hey oh-- go easy on me. Ha ha. Just kiddin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就喜欢你这种直接的性格\N{\fs38}I like your straightforward style.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这实验服的行头挺酷的\N{\fs38}And that lab coat's pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊Summer\N{\fs38}Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道我的名字\N{\fs38}He knew my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么会不知道 你长这么美\N{\fs38}Why wouldn't he? You're great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们还是小心为妙\N{\fs38}But, listen, just be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能排除任何人是吸血鬼的嫌疑\N{\fs38}We can't rule anybody out as the vampire,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男神也不行\N{\fs38}Not even the dreamboats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌\N{\fs38}Stop, tiny Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟孙子孙女杀吸血鬼去啦\N{\fs38}Huntin' a vampire with my grandkids!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小Rick[哔]无敌\N{\fs38}[bleep]tiny Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一步是观察你们的构造体\N{\fs38}The next step is to watch your mythologues
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观察他们之间的互动 "意外"的是\N{\fs38}interact together and, uh-- big surprise--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,场面从来都不好看\N{\fs38}It's never pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是Gloompfschs夫妇\N{\fs38}Here we have Garrrh and Zharbidar Gloompfschs,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换种说法\N{\fs38}Or, should I say, here we have the way
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是这对夫妇对对方的感知\N{\fs38}Garrrh and Zharbidar perceive each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明显\N{\fs38}As we can all see,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根本不是他们本来的样子\N{\fs38}This is hardly the real Garrrh and Zharbidar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这很好 因为在他们脑海里\N{\fs38}Which is good, because the relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的婚姻关系不仅丑恶\N{\fs38}In their heads is not only ugly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且难以维系\N{\fs38}It's unsustainable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可能已经学到了重要的一课\N{\fs38}You may already be learning something important--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看到的所有婚姻关系都各不相同\N{\fs38}All of these relationships are different,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不真实 而且没有一对能行的通\N{\fs38}None of them are real, and none of them work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不是对方时常认为的魔鬼模样\N{\fs38}We are not the monsters we sometimes see each other as,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们是真实的 我们是协调的\N{\fs38}Because we are real and we are functional.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为此 我们比这些怪物好多了\N{\fs38}That's what makes us better than them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能解决问题\N{\fs38}We can find solutions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能相互适应\N{\fs38}We can adapt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能相互交流\N{\fs38}We can communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是\N{\fs38}And, most importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能相互合作\N{\fs38}We can work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然颇有坎坷 最后终于苦尽甘来\N{\fs38}Well, it was a tough adventure, but it paid off --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校里没有吸血鬼啦\N{\fs38}Our school is vampire-free!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到Feratu教练竟然是吸血鬼\N{\fs38}Man, who would've suspected coach Feratu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\an8}这个名字出自著名的吸血鬼诺斯费拉图
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们做得很好 功不可没\N{\fs38}You did great, guys. Couldn't have done it without ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要为自己感到骄傲\N{\fs38}You know, we-- w-we should be proud of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们杀了一个吸血鬼 同时干掉一个体育老师\N{\fs38}We killed a vampire and a gym teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 也算一石二鸟\N{\fs38}Ha ha ha. Talk about two-for-one, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原本的身体是\N{\fs38}So, how, exactly, is your old body
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么在这里面维持生命的啊\N{\fs38}living in there, grandpa Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.62,0:06:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是高压氧量子液体\N{\fs38}Oh, you know, hyperbaric quantum fluid,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱七八糟的东西\N{\fs38}That kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以保存生物组织\N{\fs38}It preserves living tissue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没多少东西要保存的了\N{\fs38}Not that there was much to preserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那皮包骨跟木乃伊似的\N{\fs38}Look at that mummy! Ha! Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该回到那老家伙的身体里了\N{\fs38}And I guess it's time for me to get back inside the old-timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天呐Toby Matthews问我父母在不在家\N{\fs38}Oh, my god. Toby Matthews is asking if my parents
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还问我能不能开派对\N{\fs38}Are still out of town and if we can have a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒 Summer 你看我上午说什么来着\N{\fs38}All right, way to go, Summer! What did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还问小Rick会不会来\N{\fs38}Ohh! He's asking if tiny Rick will be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Summer 我转念一想\N{\fs38}Well, you know what, Summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉他 小Rick会过去的\N{\fs38}Tell him tiny Rick will be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他带点酒来\N{\fs38}And tell him to bring some brews!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 你 你会以小Rick的身份留下\N{\fs38}For real? Y-y-y-you would stay as tiny Rick,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为了留下来开派对\N{\fs38}Just so we can have a party?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 多一晚又有什么关系\N{\fs38}Hell, yeah! What's one more night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说这老家伙在这儿 谁能尽兴啊\N{\fs38}And who can have fun with this old bastard hanging around, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wubby lubby doob doob\N{\fs38}Wubby lubby doob doob!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小Rick\N{\fs38}Tiny Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 这边是Beth和Jerry Smith\N{\fs38}Moving on. Now, we have beth and jerry smith
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自地一球行星\N{\fs38}From the planet e-arth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心跳得很厉害\N{\fs38}My heart is pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会很棒\N{\fs38}This is gonna be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地一球的两性关系比较简单\N{\fs38}The e-arth relationships are simpler.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是一个原始星球 所以他们的失调状态\N{\fs38}It's a primitive planet, so their dysfunctions are oh --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 发生了什么\N{\fs38}W-wait, what? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Smith夫妇的构造体在哪\N{\fs38}Where are the smith mythologues?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊\N{\fs38}Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 天啊  - 守住那个牢房\N{\fs38}- Oh, my god. - Secure the cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁想参观一下礼品店 很有趣的\N{\fs38}Uh, hey! You know what's fun? Our gift shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们何不有序地前往\N{\fs38}Why don't we proceed in an orderly --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的老天\N{\fs38}Oh, dear god, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是互利共生的\N{\fs38}They're codependent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑\N{\fs38}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 你真的很会驾驭\N{\fs38}Oh, yeah, yeah, you really know how to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 蓝色的衣服啊  - 真的吗\N{\fs38}- sport that color blue. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你今天真的很美  - 我的天啊 \N{\fs38}- You're looking real good. - Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好 Morty  - 你好啊 Jessica\N{\fs38}- Hey, morty. Oh, hey - hey, Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 小Rick是你的亲兄弟还是表的\N{\fs38}So, is tiny Rick your brother or cousin, or...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.89,0:08:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不是 我外公把他的意识\N{\fs38}No, my grandpa just transferred
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转移到他自己的克隆体上了\N{\fs38}His consciousness into a clone of himself
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样他就可以来我们学校了\N{\fs38}So he could be in our high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅气\N{\fs38}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来看 小Rick在弹吉他\N{\fs38}Hey, tiny Rick's playing guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位朋友\N{\fs38}All right, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一首来自我的内心\N{\fs38}This next one's coming straight from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到哪儿唱到哪儿 现场发挥的歌词\N{\fs38}Making the lyrics up right off the top of my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*放我出来 你所见的*\N{\fs38}*Let me out, What you see*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*只是一个假的驱壳*\N{\fs38}*is not the  same person as me*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.38,0:08:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*我的生活是个谎言 我不是你望着的那个人*\N{\fs38}*My life's a lie, I'm not who you're looking at*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*放我出来 给我自由 我已年迈*\N{\fs38}*Let me out, set me free,I'm really old *
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*这不是真正的我*\N{\fs38}*This isn't me*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*我的身体在大缸里渐渐死亡*\N{\fs38}*My real body's slowly dying in a vat*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*有人听到我的呐喊吗 有人明白我吗*\N{\fs38}*Is anybody listening, can anyone understand*
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*别再傻盯着我了 救救我吧*\N{\fs38}*Stop Looking at me like that and actually help me*
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*救我 救救我 我要死了*\N{\fs38}*Help! Help me, I'm gonna die*
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小Rick 谢谢捧场\N{\fs38}Tiny Rick! Thanks, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙太赞了\N{\fs38}This guy's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.93,0:09:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我爱小Rick   - 帅飞了\N{\fs38}- I love tiny Rick! - Bad ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么[哔]\N{\fs38}What the [bleep]?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 你们这机构怎么搞的\N{\fs38}Yeah, I know! What kind of operation are you running?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们 你们两夫妇是什么的婚姻关系啊\N{\fs38}Us?! What the hell kind of relationship do you have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 怪在我们的头上\N{\fs38}Oh, right, blame this on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 没错 我就怪在你们头上\N{\fs38}Okay, uh, I can and I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的恶魔化构造体居然在合作\N{\fs38}Your demonized mythologizations of each other are cooperating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是好事吗\N{\fs38}Isn't that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 糟透了\N{\fs38}No. No! It's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的婚姻是我见过最糟的\N{\fs38}You have the single worst marriage I've ever witnessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不应该存在\N{\fs38}It shouldn't exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们根本完全彻底不应该在一起\N{\fs38}You should never, ever, ever, have gotten together
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还很不懂你们是怎么以及为什么\N{\fs38}And I do not understand how, or why,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会走到一起\N{\fs38}You would ever stay together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这婚姻咨询也太烂了吧\N{\fs38}Well, this is just bad couples' therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是嘛\N{\fs38}Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我们\N{\fs38}Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置只够再多一人了\N{\fs38}There's only room for one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是心理咨询师 我跟他们说说\N{\fs38}I'm a therapist. I'll talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是咨询师 马上走\N{\fs38}They're not therapists. Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有办法联系上爸爸的\N{\fs38}There's gotta be a way to contact my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们找个控制室什么的\N{\fs38}Let's find a control room or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beth 快来看看\N{\fs38}Beth! You'll want to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么\N{\fs38}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个小型可拆卸面板\N{\fs38}It's a small, hinged panel
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面有一些空间\N{\fs38}With a tiny amount of space behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你也能找到一个\N{\fs38}If you can find one, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来几个小时或几天我们就安全了\N{\fs38}We should be safe for hours, maybe days!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jerry 你在这里待好\N{\fs38}You stay put, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去求救 假如我能活着的话\N{\fs38}I'll send help, if I make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不找个地方自己躲起来吗\N{\fs38}You don't want to find your own little hatch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jerry 我相信你独自躲好的话\N{\fs38}Jerry, I believe that, if you hide by yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以活下去\N{\fs38}You might survive and I believe I,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时我也相信 我独自也能逃出这里\N{\fs38}By myself, have a shot of getting out of here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们两人一起\N{\fs38}But the two of us, together?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fs38}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能那个心理医生是对的\N{\fs38}Look, maybe the shrink was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好运\N{\fs38}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我听好了\N{\fs38}All right, now, you listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实不听也可以\N{\fs38}Oh! Or don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别 求你了\N{\fs38}Hey! Don't! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 别过来\N{\fs38}Oh, god, oh, god, oh, god!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白我以前说过什么\N{\fs38}Now, I know I've said, in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数学很重要 确实是\N{\fs38}That math is important -- and it is! --
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还认为 总有一天 你们会回想起\N{\fs38}But I also think that, one day, you'll all look back
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟小Rick和Morty做同学的日子\N{\fs38}On being in high school with tiny Rick and Morty,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为听说他们昨晚搞了一个超级棒的派对\N{\fs38}Who I hear had a great party last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 下课\N{\fs38}So, class dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放你们假\N{\fs38}You've got the day off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干的好 Goldenfold先生\N{\fs38}All right! Good work, mr. Goldenfold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 到外面转转 多读书\N{\fs38}Yeah, get outside. Read a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Danielle 涂点防晒霜\N{\fs38}Put on some sunscreen, Danielle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Summer 你好 上衣真漂亮\N{\fs38}Hey, what's up, Summer? Ooh, nice top.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 小Rick 你觉得\N{\fs38}Thanks. Tiny rick, you think you might be
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚可以回到老的身体里去吗\N{\fs38}Getting back into your old body tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行喔 今晚是舞会之夜\N{\fs38}No can do. Tonight's the big dance
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morty还会带Jessica出席 他需要这架小僚机\N{\fs38}And Morty's bringing Jessica. He needs his tiny wing man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小Rick\N{\fs38}Tiny Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚不行的话要等到什么时候\N{\fs38}Okay, but if not tonight, when?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 等我想回去了\N{\fs38}I don't know. When I feel like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别这么咄咄逼人的\N{\fs38}Damn, girl! You need to chill out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事是你先想出来的\N{\fs38}This whole thing was your idea, in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在又是你想尽快结束\N{\fs38}And, now, you're trying to rush it along.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是嘛 我喜欢高中\N{\fs38}Yeah, and you know what? I like high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢跟大家玩 小Rick万岁\N{\fs38}I like hanging out. Tiny rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果喜欢这样生活的人不是真正的你呢\N{\fs38}But what if the you that likes it isn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别傻了 Summer\N{\fs38}Oh, Summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是有个年轻驱壳的Rick\N{\fs38}It's just Rick in a younger body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会 会 会 会\N{\fs38}What's the -- what's -- what's -- what's --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有什么问题啊\N{\fs38}What's the -- what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看他的画 Morty\N{\fs38}Look at his art, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最近走情绪摇滚风\N{\fs38}I've got an emo streak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是我这么酷炫的部分原因\N{\fs38}It's part of what makes me so rad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这里写着"救救我 Morty和Summer"\N{\fs38}Why does it say "Help me morty and summer!"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Summer 这是画的题目\N{\fs38}Come on, Summer, that's the title of the art.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么<霹雳游侠>叫霹雳游侠\N{\fs38}Why was knight rider called knight rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\an8}<霹雳游侠> 80年代电视剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车的名字明明是Kitt 被人开的不是Michael Knight.\N{\fs38}The car's name was kitt. Nobody rode Michael Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\an8}男主名叫Michael Knight
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想多了 Summer 我是小Rick\N{\fs38}You're overthinking it, summer. I'm tiny rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外公 我觉得 你把意识\N{\fs38}Grandpa, I think that, when you put your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放进这个年轻的躯体了\N{\fs38}Into this body's young brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就做年轻人做的事\N{\fs38}It did what young brains do --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这副躯体把坏的想法压在心底\N{\fs38}It shoved the bad thoughts into the back
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.62,0:12:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩藏起来\N{\fs38}And put a wall around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那些想法属于真正的Rick\N{\fs38}But those bad thoughts are the real Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经年迈的事实\N{\fs38}The fact that you're old, the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终有一天会死的事实\N{\fs38}We're all going to die, one day, the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙很大 任何事都很渺小的事实\N{\fs38}The universe is so big, nothing in it matters,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些事实才造就真正的你\N{\fs38}Those facts are who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以真正的Rick被困住了\N{\fs38}So you're trapped in there and you can only
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只能通过小Rick的青少年焦虑表现出来\N{\fs38}Come out in the form of tiny rick's teen angst!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:12:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Summer 我听说\N{\fs38}Well, Summer, I hear
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toby Matthews 不喜欢神经兮兮瞎分析的女孩\N{\fs38}Toby Matthews isn't into psycho chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人喜欢这类女孩\N{\fs38}Can't think of anyone that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞会上见啦 兔崽子们 小Rick万岁\N{\fs38}I'll see you mother at the dance! Tiny rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morty 你要帮我\N{\fs38}Morty, you have to help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Summer 他很开心 我也很开心 \N{\fs38}Summer, he's happy! I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的目的吗\N{\fs38}I-I-is that why you're doing this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让我们开心\N{\fs38}You don't want me and rick to be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N{\fs38}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就把你这些逼事儿收拾收拾\N{\fs38}Well, then get your shit together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全收起来放到书包里\N{\fs38}Get it all together and put it in a backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的逼事儿 好好收拾收拾\N{\fs38}All your shit, so it's together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想把它们带走\N{\fs38}And if you gotta take it somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快带走 懂吗\N{\fs38}Take it somewhere, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带到逼事儿店卖了\N{\fs38}Take it to the shit store and sell it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者在逼事儿博物馆展览 我不管\N{\fs38}O-or put it in a shit museum. I don't care what you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 收拾好你的破逼事儿\N{\fs38}You just gotta get it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾好\N{\fs38}Get your shit together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来\N{\fs38}Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 不是吧\N{\fs38}Wait, for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是Beth对我的看法\N{\fs38}You're how Beth sees me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fs38}Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转过身去\N{\fs38}Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说转过身去\N{\fs38}I said turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beth怎么会这样想我\N{\fs38}How can beth have these thoughts about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个狗眼看人低的贱人\N{\fs38}That judgmental monster bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不接受\N{\fs38}I'm not taking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我的妻子在哪\N{\fs38}I want to know where my wife is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要协助我\N{\fs38}You are going to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停 别再这样了\N{\fs38}No! Nobody's doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动\N{\fs38}Stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干嘛\N{\fs38}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更多Jerry\N{\fs38}Jerrys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要Jerry\N{\fs38}You want jerry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不想要Jerry\N{\fs38}I don't even want jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要很多Jerry\N{\fs38}I want Jerrys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一支Jerry军队\N{\fs38}An army.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jerry军队\N{\fs38}An army of jerrys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的顺从的价值都浪费在你身上了\N{\fs38}The value of his subservience is wasted on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要利用它来征服宇宙\N{\fs38}I will use it to dominate the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 Jerry肯定觉得\N{\fs38}Ah ha ha. Boy, Jerry must think
