Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 你怎么想的 你想\N{\fs38}So, what do you think? You wanna
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱俩再维持这段婚姻一段时间不\N{\fs38}Keep this marriage going a while longer?
